Shop Store Project
This is a Spring Boot project for managing a shop store with JWT authentication and an H2 in-memory database.

Features
User authentication using JWT (JSON Web Tokens)
CRUD operations for managing products
Role-based access control (RBAC) for managing user permissions
H2 in-memory database for storing user and product data
Technologies Used
Java
Spring Boot
Spring Security
Spring Data JPA
H2 Database
JSON Web Tokens (JWT)
Maven
