API Endpoints
/api/auth/signup: Register a new user
/api/auth/signin: Authenticate user and generate JWT token
/api/products: Get all products (GET), Create new product (POST)
/api/products/{id}: Get product by ID (GET), Update product by ID (PUT), Delete product by ID (DELETE)
Configuration
JWT Secret Key: You can configure the JWT secret key and expiration time in the application.properties file.
Database Configuration: The project is configured to use an H2 in-memory database by default. You can modify the database configuration in the application.properties file if needed.
